message.body: What time for dinner tonight and what can I bring? Treats, wine, beer, all of the above?
Well rubys bedtime is 6:30-7. So if you want to catch her id say 5:30/6 but you'll need to entertain yourself for 20 mins while I put her to bed. Otherwise, 7:30? And wine sounds good!!
Great! I'll be there between 5:30 and 6 so I can see that lil boo. Let me know if you anything else!
I should be there in 20 minutes!
